name: end=beginning
description:
Made in a week for the Brackeys Game Jam 2023.1!

This isometric puzzle game will test your thinking skills!  The movement takes some time to get used to, but you can use WASD or the arrow keys. You start on the green tile and need to collect all coins in order to turn it into the yellow goal tile. All other tiles disappear after you step on them. Everything else is explained in the game itself.
